    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行股价上涨，得益于证券交易和法国零售业复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/socgen-beat-fueled-by-securities-trading-french-retail-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行第三季度的业绩远超分析师预期，因为其投资银行家从更高的交易收入中获利，且这家法国零售银行的业绩出现转机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/socgen-beat-fueled-by-securities-trading-french-retail-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元兑美元上涨，因日本央行仍有可能再次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/yen-stays-in-tight-range-vs-dollar-after-boj-holds-pat-on-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继日本央行维持利率不变之后，日元兑美元汇率在一周内首次上涨，市场关注日本央行行长上田和夫今天下午的新闻发布会，寻找未来加息的暗示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/yen-stays-in-tight-range-vs-dollar-after-boj-holds-pat-on-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台风康蕾袭击台湾，上海迎来暴雨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/taiwan-braces-for-super-typhoon-kong-rey-after-shutting-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台风康蕾携带危险大风登陆台湾，随着大型风暴朝中国大陆移动，上海将迎来自 1981 年以来 11 月份最强降雨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/taiwan-braces-for-super-typhoon-kong-rey-after-shutting-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下跌，日元走强，日本央行维持利率不变：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四亚洲股市下跌，因强劲的经济数据使美联储即将降息的前景变得模糊。日本央行公布利率决定后，日元走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 22:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>增长最快的主要经济体所吹嘘的消费故事正在破裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/from-reliance-to-unilever-firms-worry-about-low-consumer-demand-in-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度生产从肥皂到汽车等各种产品的消费品公司正在敲响警钟：由于通货膨胀和失业影响市场情绪，城市中产阶级支出一年多来一直低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/from-reliance-to-unilever-firms-worry-about-low-consumer-demand-in-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>锂业困境导致中国主要生产商今年迄今亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/lithium-woes-leave-top-china-producers-with-year-to-date-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电池金属市场低迷持续挤压锂行业，中国两大锂生产商今年前九个月仍处于亏损状态。]]></description>
